  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA20">
<l>paḻipāvaṅ kaiyakaṟṟip palkālu niṉṉai</l>
<l>vaḻivāḻvār vāḻvarā mātō – vaḻuviṉṟi</l>
<l>nāraṇaṉṟaṉ ṉāmaṅka ṇaṉkuṇarntu naṉkēttuṅ</l>
<l>kāraṇaṅka ṭāmuṭaiyār tām</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Warding off sin [and] evil with [their] hands, those who live [with] you</l>
<l>as the path for a long time, won’t they live?</l>
<l>It is them who possess the means to perceive well without fault</l>
<l>the names of Nāraṇaṉ [and] to praise [him] well.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
